{"tid":2056752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛：歐洲緩和但全球新型肺炎疫情正在惡化","createTime":"2020-06-09T02:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T02:17:19.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"048ca3fc275628e499336df7907e44ef00619dea","tid":2056752,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"世衛：歐洲緩和但全球新型肺炎疫情正在惡化<br />\n2020-06-09 HKT 05:27<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織形容，歐洲疫情緩和，但全球疫情正在惡化。<br />\n<br />\n世衛總幹事譚德塞在日內瓦表示，日前全球匯報超過13萬宗確診新型肺炎，是單日新高，大部分在美洲和南亞。東歐和中亞部分地區的病例數字亦不斷上升。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞促請各國，繼續密切監測疫情發展，特別是部分國家恢復舉行各種大規模集會，必須確保疫情不會反彈。<br />\n<br />\n針對近期全球的反種族歧視活動，世衛建議參與者，盡可能與他人保持至少1米距離，注意清潔雙手、咳嗽時掩住口鼻及戴上口罩等。<br />\n<br />\n他又強調，追蹤病例接觸者、隔離同檢測，仍是疫情應對的最基本措施。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530944-20200609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530944-20200609.htm&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19vMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=ecb39511\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530944-20200609.htm&h=d361222a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530944-20200609.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dbeac43985f3b34bdbde8da1b8fbe8a653467988","tid":2056752,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"屌仲信佢就傻仔"},{"pid":"26869203606a6cad031820042f833625aba8d4e6","tid":2056752,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"力架無一個是蘑菇的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74de119b22d4298d44ff7b5ba24a6fb7bd3ac4f0","tid":2056752,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"見到咸濕蔡個撚樣就想中柒佢"},{"pid":"ae6efa50c94d4c250a58d350a06264bf7c19edc4","tid":2056752,"uid":30028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:14: